channel.title: Weird problem
channel.description:
Hey, Yesterday I've downloaded RSCD v25 source,and installed it succesfully on my computer. This morning I was finishing stuff on it,like setting the last configurations etc,and whenever I run: Run_Lserver and run_server it says:
Error unable to login. Unrecognised response code.
Maybe this is the problem causing it:
Whenever I start Run_Lserver and then Run_Server I lose connection in like 5-10 minutes. I don't know why,but I setted everything right,ports etc.
Anyone help me please? :D
